<p><strong>Marika's Hammer</strong>&nbsp;is a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Hammers" href="/Hammers">Hammer</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. The <strong>Marika's Hammer</strong>&nbsp;scales primarily with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Strength" href="/Strength">Strength</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith">Faith</a>&nbsp;and is a good <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Weapons" href="/Weapons" target="">Weapon</a> for heavy attacks that deal holy damage.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Stone hammer made in the lands of the Numen, outside the Lands Between. The tool with which Queen Marika shattered the Elden Ring and Radagon attempted to repair it.</em></p> 
 <p><em>The hammer partially broke upon shattering the Ring, becoming splintered with rune fragments.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to Find&nbsp;Marika's Hammer in&nbsp;Elden Ring</h3> 
<p>The Marika's Hammer weapon can be found at the following location:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li> <p>Trade <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Elden Remembrance" href="/Elden+Remembrance">Elden Remembrance</a> with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Enia" href="/Enia">Enia</a> at <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Roundtable Hold" href="/Roundtable+Hold">Roundtable Hold</a>.</p> </li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring Marika's Hammer Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Weapon <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Skills" href="/Skills" target="">Skill</a>: <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Gold Breaker" href="/Gold+Breaker">Gold Breaker</a></li> 
 <li>This weapon&nbsp;cannot be infused with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ashes of War" href="/Ashes+of+War" target="">Ashes of War</a></li> 
 <li><strong>Marika's Hammer</strong> can be upgraded by using <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Somber Smithing Stones" href="/Somber+Smithing+Stones">Somber Smithing Stones</a></li> 
 <li>Sell Value:&nbsp;&nbsp;<img title="Runes" src="/file/Elden-Ring/er-runes-13.png" alt="er runes 13" width="18" height="18">&nbsp;1000</li> 
 <li>Other notes and player tips go here</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Moveset &amp; Videos in&nbsp;Elden Ring for&nbsp;Marika's Hammer</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Videos for the Marika's Hammer Coming Soon</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Marika's Hammer Upgrades in Elden Ring</h3> 
<p>Please see the&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Upgrades" href="/Upgrades" target="">Upgrades</a>&nbsp;page to understand the weapon bolstering process.</p> 
<p>Requires regular reinforcement with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Somber Smithing Stones" href="/Somber+Smithing+Stones" target="">Somber Smithing Stones</a></p> 
<p>This upgrade can be enchanted with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Magic Spells" href="/Magic+Spells" target="">Magic</a>&nbsp;or boosted with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Consumables" href="/Consumables" target="">Consumables</a>.</p> 
